Class TestBasicFunctionality

Object
  TestBasicFunctionality

public class TestBasicFunctionality
extends Object

A class to test the basic functionality of DungAF.

This class tests -

  • DungAF's constructors;
  • methods which modify the AFs recorded by DungAF objects;
  • methods concerning the comparison of DungAF objects;
  • methods concerning conflict between arguments;
  • methods concerning the acceptability of arguments with respect to sets of arguments;
  • getRandomDungAF(int, int, int, int, Collection<String>); and
  • recordsExtsOfType(String).

This class must be run with assertions enabled.
